 sc0 ls0 ws0">如果没有这样，<span class="_ _6"></span>就随意揣测、<span class="_ _6"></span>妄加评论，<span class="_ _6"></span>肯定与真相有一定</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yb1 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">的距离。 </div><div class="t m0 x9 h6 y17b ff7 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">                                        <span class="_ _2"></span>                                        <span class="_ _2"></span>                                      <span class="_ _5"></span> </div><div class="t m0 x9 h10 y17c ffd fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">评价元朝的皇帝们，个个英武沉毅，虽然大多命数不长，却都豁达大度，颇有</div><div class="t m0 x9 h10 y163 ffd fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">君主之气。如云：<span class="_ _12"></span>“元有天下，其疆域之袤，<span class="_ _d"></span>海漕之富，兵力物力之雄廓，过于</div><div class="t m0 x9 h10 y164 ffd fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">汉唐。自塞外三帝，中原七帝，皆英武踵立，无一童昏暴缪之主。<span class="_ _12"></span>”<span class="ff7"> </span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
